Output docs/default-toon.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1400
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Set Padding 16

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 500ms
Type "rak internal/counting"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 4s

Sleep 2s

Type "rak --human internal/counting"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
